, and every creature on land or sea who hears his voice seeks forgiveness for him.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6202 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/07\/allah-descends-praying\/","url_meta":{"origin":20784,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tahajjud: Allah descends for those praying at night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Rifa'ah ibn 'Arabah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen a half or third of the night has passed, Allah descends to the lowest heaven, and He says, 'My servants do not ask from anyone but Me. Who is asking Me that I might give him?\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40474,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/07\/created-to-forgive\/","url_meta":{"origin":20784,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: Allah created you to forgive you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe expiation of sin is regret. If you never sinned, Allah Almighty would surely come with people who would sin, and He would forgive them.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2623 Grade:\u00a0Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/20784","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=20784"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/20784\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=20784"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=20784"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=20784"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}